Cheetor



He ran and jumped between Iris and Prowl.


Cheetor:



"fight me.I AM TRANSFORMED."


Cheetor was already in robot mode. He was transforming into a better 
mode. A battle mode. He turned from six feet tall to eight foot two 
inches. His beast face came over his beast mode like a helmet or a 
mask. His cat claws came over each finger. He stood there waiting for 
Iris to make a move.
